Mi Familia, 
Cuando se está Lejos de tu familia, es un dolor muy grande. Muchos latinos que Emigran lo entienden , pero me siento muy agradecida por la oportunidad de volver a mi querido país , Colombia 🇨🇴 y compartir un hermoso momento con mis familiares . Al final , 
“La felicidad es para Compartirla”

Family, when you are far away from your family is so difficult, immigrants, understand 😞-
I feel so Grateful for the Opportunity to comeback to my beautiful country, Colombia 🇨🇴 and spend time with my family and share happiness- because ,
“Happiness is only real when Shared”

Victoria, My Dear Daughter, Pray with Me : 

Lord, I offer You all of Me , all that I am and all that I am Not .
I offer You every Good decision and Every regrettable Mistake ; every great accomplishment and every missed Opportunity. Every Divinely inspired gift and Every unapplied talent; every Success and every failure. I offer You all Joy and all Heartache, every Kindness and every bitterness to be forgotten, every twinkle in my eye and every tear flowing down my cheek. Every great Love and each lost act of charity; all things holy and good in me and all things in need of greater purification. I give you every joyful memory and every pain , every laugh and all misery mixed with weeping. I give you Lord , every Healthy breath and every weakness of mind and body, every restful repose and every anxious sleepless night- 
O Lord , you can have all of Me , the beauty that You’ve deposited deep within Me and the Emptiness of my Sinful Faults. I love You and I am Yours Completely. Amen .
